reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nothing fancy, they will do the job
reviews.reviewText: I'm using this to store thumb drives! Surprise! It holds 15 in neat little pockets, and there also a zipped mesh pouch where you can put other miscellaneous stuff.These look fairly durable, but I've seen nicer, more expensive ones in stores that look more durable. If you're like me and are just going to have this on your desk or in your desk drawer, I doubt that you'll wear it out.At the price, they're a great deal.
